ualifying Rounds|FA Cup Qualifying Rounds]], One appearance in the [[FA Trophy]]</ref> | 0 | 28 | 0 |- | [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] | [[2017–18 in English football|2017–18]]<ref name="Games played by Will Norris in 2017/2018">{{Soccerbase season|71366|2017| accessdate = 12 July 2017}}</ref> | [[EFL Championship|Championship]] | 1 | 0 | 2 | 0 | 4 | 0 | colspan="2" | — | 7 | 0 |- !colspan="3" | Career total ! 185 ! 0 ! 8 ! 0 ! 5 ! 0 ! 35 ! 0 ! 233 ! 0 |}
